      "title": "Inflation rose to 54.6 percent",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Valuation and Statistics, inflation in the country rose to 54.6 percent in June.",
        "Accordingly, food inflation rose to 80.1 per cent and non-food inflation to 42.4 per cent.",
        "In addition, transportation inflation rose to 128 percent and clothing and footwear inflation to 44.4 percent."
      ],
